eckout流程\n\n### 3. **异常特征**\n- **无Fast Fail现象**：所有服务都在响应，但延迟极高\n- **无连接拒绝**：服务可用但性能严重下降\n- **最下游异常**：productcatalogservice作为最底层服务出现最大延迟，是根因而非受害者\n\n### 4. **拓扑验证**\n根据系统调用拓扑，productcatalogservice确实是最下游服务之一（仅依赖TiDB），其异常会向上游传播到所有依赖它的服务，符合根因定位原则。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "productcatalogservice is the root cause due to severe latency spikes in GetProduct operations"}
